MAMELODI Sundowns supporters will be waiting with bated breath to find out whether their players have scored big at the glittering Caf Awards ceremony in Abuja, Nigeria, tonight. Denis Onyango and Khama Billiat are nominated in the category of African Player of the Year, Based in Africa.Sundows coach Pitso Mosimane was nominated as Coach of the Year, while Downs were also nominated for Team of the Year.Sundowns dominated and conquered the African continent when, against all odds, they lifted the Caf Champions League trophy after defeating Zamalek in the finals. Sundowns were initially eliminated from Caf competitions twice but the football gods came to their rescue.CONTINUED ON PAGE 31